pan><br />\n<br />\n而家冇市佔就梗係要零手續費吸客啦，到有翻咁上下市佔你估佢收唔收你錢？ (參考下香港同深圳東江水價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 肯撚定加你手續費再同你講要不是中國你錢都冇得俾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 今天微信、支付寶可以以極快的速度在全球擴張。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你個國家限住人民用銀聯支那寶，咁外國咪只好喺旅遊景點收銀聯支那寶方便你囉，講到尾客戶群咪又係得支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋香港人有得用VISA/Master/Amex，去到外國做乜要用八達通？八達通又點解要推去全世界？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 支付寶、微信錢包可以將錢放在貨幣基金，提供年化4-7厘回報。</span><br />\n<br />\n喺唔喺存款保障計劃入面先？冇就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1940c63d1705ada1f77556605d287110ae8d1e65","tid":494305,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:34:06.000Z","msg":"煩閪夠未，真係好閪煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0552ad0aeb51b49bf4700cd75b248e6cd7b68a42","tid":494305,"uid":72693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T22:35:06.000Z","msg":"要上網先係最危險<br />\n你睇隔離btc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2b4e7679f760b90c004c3ac87d08313ecb9308","tid":494305,"uid":26322,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T23:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">總之支那嘢就唔撚用</span></blockquote><br />\n試下全身可以除淨幾多野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就覺得支那做既衫連染料都會致癌<br />\n<br />\n利身，家中用品全部made in japan, made in usa, made in thailand/malaysia/vietnam/cambodia/bangladesh<br />\n<br />\n你呢？"},{"pid":"186a39b07e3ede449c6ad2c9c4084e38ab6fdd17","tid":494305,"uid":126510,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017