ail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F075516_04a1d03c61559856b6e8a982c42b9387.jpg&h=f6b478d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff6c8db894ccc9ef8ac53d2dc15434ba852679a0","tid":494305,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:07:24.000Z","msg":"移動支付咁點解我唔用apple pay link信用卡比？"},{"pid":"45c7203cfa8160814e8a3ffd5a48fa43beb2e0e0","tid":494305,"uid":157442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:08:20.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔反對用移動支付 我淨係反對用支付寶 一陣比中共經濟封鎖delete data我咪渣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330699fcd8efc50980833412b93e44ea4f4fb598","tid":494305,"uid":470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:34:23.000Z","msg":"睇到假幣已經知篇文係垃圾<br />\n邊度都會有假幣，但要睇嚴重程度<br />\n支那最高面值係$100就唔嚴重完全係廢話<br />\n支那人連$20都驗屍咁撚驗，你話嚴唔嚴重呀？<br />\n<br />\n所以話崇支嘅一係扮瞓，一係係無乜去過支那"},{"pid":"8f8e223a6de3570de53a3aab1aa41caf8c1b5059","tid":494305,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>必需internet先落後呀，條友倒轉啲嘢諗，online 同offline payment都支援先叫先進，否則一冇internet 連接就乜都唔駛做啦</blockquote><br />\n我都奇怪緊<br />\n一定要連internet 代表好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢諗嗰種先進只講方便，冇理會可靠度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無internet 就用唔到已經係唔可靠啦</blockquote><br />\n佢個意思應該係支付寶剩係需要上網<br />\n八達通要上網加部機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜小巴部八達通機有上網既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb540d586a62f326de601d75416cbb28bb99452","tid":494305,"uid":57297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港有一種講法是：內地移動支付迅速普及是因為內地假幣多。這個說法很可笑。<span style=\"color: red;\">內地有假幣，香港難道沒有？</span>香港也多次出現1000元和500元假幣，時至今日，很多商鋪仍然不敢收1000元紙幣。內地當然也傳出多次假幣案件，但內地的貨幣總量比香港多出很多倍，究竟誰的假幣比率更高，還不好說。反過來我也可以說，內地紙幣最大面值才100元，相對而言香港收到假幣的潛在損失比內地大幾倍，<span style=\"color: red;\">為什麼不是香港的移動支付更普及呢？ </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個駁論好垃圾，轉移視線，假銀紙冇促進電子付款發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本邏輯謬誤嚟<br />\n<br />\n佢完全有意忽略香港同大陸發生假幣事件嘅概率<br />\n<br />\n如果香港一單嘅概率等於大陸發生一千單嘅概率<br />\n<br />\n咁邊個潛在損失大啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb17ec0f3c6754fc3e4e60df42102ad048366b00","tid":494305,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d64f5a3ffe028c00b473c498b8ead598d689e993","tid":494305,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T01:13:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acec3c28cb7b15386ccde84a571215b773fc1f8e","tid":494305,"uid":39846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T01:13:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係好嘢就唔洗兩三日岀一篇飛機文洗腦啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我未見過有專家勸人用visa，八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41382cbaf7deae4fff760fc09284ba2e6d2aee0f","tid":494305,"uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T01:21:40.000Z","msg":"有假幣都唔會公開知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新聞撚會報導咩"},{"pid":"4b973276f10d63fd431f8ffb6a2cee5321920fa0","tid":494305,"uid":26528,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T01:22:47.000Z","msg":"1.香港小型商鋪唔收一千蚊係因為找唔到出去先係主要原因。<br />\n2.我唔用cash，我用credit/debit card會安全過你微信好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.1.香港card payment的確係無噤快同方便，好似外國噤有得拍卡重要普及性就贏過你微信n倍啦.<br />\n3.微信同paypal比一比就已經差幾皮"},{"pid":"0ce0c8b84cb4f77db4429ed21e7cd6aa0b119229","tid":494305